[application]

config/name="Project Boost"
config/description="Now a little bit more polished, with the player being instanced in the level and being actively controllable, albeit movement is limited. I'm calling this V0.2 since it seems like a big improvement from the last update.

- V0.3: Now uses torque and force to move the player, and also has rigid body physics, of course. Currently playable, so I'm going to start publishing exported projects.
- V0.35: Now has a gameplay loop! When you hit the floor, you go back to the start; When you reach the green platform, the game ends! Pretty neat, but wait until you get to read the messages for landings and the likes."
config/version="0.35"
run/main_scene="uid://c41qqpgk3iuau"
config/features=PackedStringArray("4.6", "Forward Plus")
config/icon="uid://rpyspug527pc"

